Silvano Fashion Profit Soars on Higher Lingerie Demand in Russia

-- B y   O t t   U m m e l a s
-- 
2011-02-16T07:58:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/silvano-fashion-profit-soars-on-higher-lingerie-demand-in-russia.html
AS Silvano Fashion Group, the
second-largest listed Baltic clothing company, reported higher
fourth-quarter profit on rising lingerie demand in  Russia  and
the Baltic countries.  Net income increased to 2.6 million euros ($3.5 million)
from 326,000 euros a year earlier, the Tallinn-based company
said in a regulatory statement late yesterday. Revenue rose 25
percent to 20.9 million euros.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ott Ummelas in Tallinn at 
 oummelas@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at 
 wmorris@bloomberg.net  